# Root build context for r-engine:
# keep context minimal to avoid sending the full repo.
**

# Keep Docker config and r-engine runtime files
!.dockerignore
!services/r-engine/
!services/r-engine/Dockerfile
!services/r-engine/app.R

# Keep single shared R analysis source
!services/api/
!services/api/r/
!services/api/r/analysis.R
